            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1">
                <p xml:lang="heb">
               <supplied reason="lost">תתניח</supplied> נפשה דשאבה<lb/>
               <supplied reason="lost">בר</supplied>
               <gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="2"/>ום קשיש דמית בה<lb/>
               <supplied reason="lost">ביו</supplied>ם חמישה
                        בעסרין<lb/>
               <supplied reason="lost">יו</supplied>מין בירח אלול,
                    בשתה<lb/>תליתיתא די שבועה<lb/>דהיא שנת ארבע מא<lb/>וארבעין וארבע שנין<lb/>לחרבן
                    בית מקדשה<lb/>שלום על ישרא<supplied reason="lost">ל</supplied> שלום</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>[Rested be] the soul of Sabah?<lb/>[son of ..]wm? (the Elder) who died on the
                    5th?<lb/>[on] the fifth [day] (Thursday), on the twentieth<lb/>[d]ay of the
                    month E(lul), in the<lb/>third year of the seven-year cycle<lb/>which is the
                    year four hundred<lb/>and forty-four years<lb/>of the destruction of the
                    Sanctuary.<lb/>Peace upon Israel. Peace.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>Many letters and words are in parentheses, added by editor, for no clear reason.
                    Much of the inscription readings are of low certainty. Dated to 20 Elul (?) 444
                    E.D.S., 3rd S.Y. = 513 C.E.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
